          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Spectrum of the beta delayed alpha-particle"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-Abstract:  the absolute cross section for the",
                "radiative capture reaction 7-Be(p,gamma)8-B at the",
                "center-of-mass energies E = 0.32 to 2.61 MeV has been",
                "measured using a 7-Be target deposited on a Cu backing",
                "and observing the beta-delayed alpha-particles from",
                "8-B.  The backing causes a loss of less than 1% of the",
                "8-B residual nuclides.  The resulting astrophysical",
                "S(E) factor at zero energy, S(0) = 18.4+/-1.6 eV*B, is",
                "consistent only with a restricted data set from",
                "previous work."
              ]
            }
          ],
